00:25:15,740 --> 00:25:25,230
[Room 608 Chen Xi]

289
00:25:18,540 --> 00:25:19,380
Who did it?

290
00:25:19,970 --> 00:25:21,060
It wasn't you?

291
00:25:22,780 --> 00:25:24,660
I told Dai Wei that it must be you.

292
00:25:24,660 --> 00:25:25,850
Now you're telling me you have no idea.

293
00:25:27,140 --> 00:25:29,180
You know we came so close

294
00:25:29,850 --> 00:25:31,820
to grabbing Liao Yongjia's foxtail.

295
00:25:32,940 --> 00:25:34,690
I thought you were calm enough,

296
00:25:34,820 --> 00:25:36,180
but still, you got played by Liao Yongjia.

297
00:25:36,180 --> 00:25:36,820
Chen Mo,

298
00:25:40,980 --> 00:25:44,340
the police suspect that you're involved in multiple murder,

299
00:25:44,340 --> 00:25:46,060
robbery, and homicide cases.

300
00:25:46,220 --> 00:25:47,980
Please go to the police station with me for investigation.

301
00:25:48,130 --> 00:25:49,500
Are your policemen's last name Lai?

302
00:25:49,740 --> 00:25:51,260
Who saw us at the crime scene?

303
00:25:51,300 --> 00:25:52,420
Who is talking to you?

304
00:25:52,700 --> 00:25:53,300
You.

305
00:25:55,060 --> 00:25:55,980
I've been there indeed.

306
00:25:56,620 --> 00:25:57,820
But I went there to save my daughter.

307
00:25:58,540 --> 00:25:59,690
Then how do you explain this?

308
00:26:03,100 --> 00:26:04,140
It was found at the scene,

309
00:26:04,140 --> 00:26:05,140
with your fingerprint on it.

310
00:26:09,130 --> 00:26:10,540
I want to have a few words with my daughter.

311
00:26:12,060 --> 00:26:12,740
Hurry up.

312
00:26:40,180 --> 00:26:41,380
Take care of Xi for me.

313
00:27:11,500 --> 00:27:12,660
He has a daughter.

314
00:27:12,660 --> 00:27:14,260
It is not written in his file, isn't it?

315
00:27:15,980 --> 00:27:16,580
It's not.

316
00:27:17,660 --> 00:27:19,180
How about I look into his daughter?

317
00:27:21,620 --> 00:27:24,700
I feel like Xiang has become a stranger to me.

318
00:27:30,060 --> 00:27:32,540
You're facing some serious charges right now.

319
00:27:33,540 --> 00:27:34,820
Kidnap. Murder.

320
00:27:35,380 --> 00:27:36,420
Drug trade.

321
00:27:37,940 --> 00:27:39,490
The police will definitely

322
00:27:39,490 --> 00:27:41,020
investigate you thoroughly.

323
00:27:41,810 --> 00:27:42,820
But you don't need to worry.

324
00:27:44,500 --> 00:27:45,780
It's just a process.

325
00:27:51,540 --> 00:27:54,460
Who shot my daughter?

326
00:27:55,300 --> 00:27:56,540
We will find that out.

327
00:27:57,180 --> 00:27:58,940
Now we will take you into custody

328
00:27:59,500 --> 00:28:02,300
for unlawful possession of firearms.

329
00:28:03,500 --> 00:28:06,810
I will give you a new job after a while.

330
00:28:07,220 --> 00:28:08,180
No problem.

331
00:28:09,020 --> 00:28:10,140
The longer I am kept in custody, the better.

332
00:28:10,940 --> 00:28:12,140
But I have a request.

333
00:28:12,740 --> 00:28:13,620
I hope that Officer Su can be there

334
00:28:13,700 --> 00:28:16,020
with Xi this whole time.

335
00:28:17,730 --> 00:28:20,700
Don't you want to go home soon to see your daughter?

336
00:28:20,740 --> 00:28:21,500
Yes, I do.

337
00:28:22,060 --> 00:28:24,420
But right now I need to stop Liang Long

338
00:28:24,420 --> 00:28:25,780
from suspecting me.

339
00:28:26,100 --> 00:28:27,980
Now if I get closer to Xi,

340
00:28:28,300 --> 00:28:29,490
it will be more dangerous for her.

341
00:28:31,060 --> 00:28:32,260
Oh, and... Officer Liao,

342
00:28:32,580 --> 00:28:33,780
after the task is accomplished,

343
00:28:35,170 --> 00:28:37,340
don't forget to clear my criminal records.

344
00:28:39,020 --> 00:28:40,340
I don't need you to teach me that.

345
00:28:43,780 --> 00:28:45,980
Where were you when Da Hui died?

346
00:28:48,980 --> 00:28:50,660
During the chaos, the gas barrel was hit

347
00:28:50,860 --> 00:28:51,820
and exploded.

348
00:28:52,180 --> 00:28:54,340
We jumped into the river and got separated.

349
00:28:58,060 --> 00:28:58,900
Officer Liao,

350
00:29:02,420 --> 00:29:05,340
you're not suspecting me of killing Da Hui, are you?

351
00:29:37,060 --> 00:29:37,980
What do you want to talk about?

352
00:29:40,300 --> 00:29:42,700
This is a bullet from a MSG90 sniper rifle.

353
00:29:44,020 --> 00:29:45,980
It shouldn't be seen in Hua City.

354
00:29:46,610 --> 00:29:47,860
I found it at the crime scene.

355
00:29:49,940 --> 00:29:51,860
You have that rifle now, don't you?

356
00:29:55,780 --> 00:29:56,740
Are you suspecting me?

357
00:30:00,140 --> 00:30:01,260
No, I'm not.

358
00:30:02,820 --> 00:30:04,340
I heard a rumor that some cop

359
00:30:05,220 --> 00:30:06,820
took a bribe when Kuntuo and Pala

360
00:30:07,580 --> 00:30:09,090
were making the deal.

361
00:30:10,500 --> 00:30:11,410
I suspect there is a mole

362
00:30:11,740 --> 00:30:13,740
in the police force as well.

363
00:30:14,260 --> 00:30:15,300
If there is not,

364
00:30:15,540 --> 00:30:16,580
Kuntuo wouldn't be able to escape

365
00:30:16,580 --> 00:30:18,300
under the circumstances.

366
00:30:18,300 --> 00:30:19,810
He must have gotten some help from the police.

367
00:30:20,500 --> 00:30:22,900
I think Luo Xiang's death

368
00:30:22,900 --> 00:30:24,180
has something to do with this too.

369
00:30:25,740 --> 00:30:26,660
So all the officers at the scene then

370
00:30:27,460 --> 00:30:29,580
are suspects.

371
00:30:30,380 --> 00:30:32,620
That's why I started the Dark Night Project.

372
00:30:35,020 --> 00:30:37,220
Since you distrust me this much,

373
00:30:37,500 --> 00:30:39,020
I'll go back and bring you all the reports.

374
00:30:39,020 --> 00:30:40,410
You handle it yourself, okay?

375
00:30:49,420 --> 00:30:50,940
Your work is finished, right?

376
00:30:51,420 --> 00:30:53,060
But we haven't found the killer.

377
00:30:54,380 --> 00:30:56,420
Maybe it's Liang Long. Maybe it's Tai.

378
00:30:57,140 --> 00:30:59,860
Or it could be anyone related to drugs.

379
00:31:00,820 --> 00:31:03,300
Our goal is to eliminate drugs.

380
00:31:04,020 --> 00:31:05,060
Let other departments figure out

381
00:31:05,060 --> 00:31:07,180
who the killer is.

382
00:31:11,490 --> 00:31:12,740
But there is only one truth.

383
00:31:14,540 --> 00:31:15,900
The person who said that to you

384
00:31:16,020 --> 00:31:17,580
must have never lived in Hua City.

385
00:31:27,580 --> 00:31:28,780
This case is closed.

386
00:31:35,160 --> 00:31:36,840
[Investigations Room]

387
00:31:37,700 --> 00:31:38,700
How's the investigation?

388
00:31:39,900 --> 00:31:42,580
The informant payment you received is from his personal assets.

389
00:31:45,180 --> 00:31:46,860
A policeman who is retiring

390
00:31:47,780 --> 00:31:49,300
can spend 2 million

391
00:31:49,700 --> 00:31:50,780
without even blinking an eye?

392
00:31:51,780 --> 00:31:52,980
Three years ago,

393
00:31:52,980 --> 00:31:54,900
Liao Yongjia sold his house

394
00:31:55,340 --> 00:31:56,460
in order to get treatment for his wife.

395
00:31:56,740 --> 00:31:59,610
It has nothing to do with those four policemen.

396
00:32:01,380 --> 00:32:02,260
So

397
00:32:02,970 --> 00:32:05,980
what he told me is true.

398
00:32:07,380 --> 00:32:09,020
After the abandoned shipyard case,

399
00:32:09,580 --> 00:32:11,500
Liao Yongjia has become very cautious.

400
00:32:11,620 --> 00:32:14,530
He seems to know that someone is investigating him.

401
00:32:15,060 --> 00:32:15,940
I have talked to the superiors

402
00:32:15,940 --> 00:32:17,300
about him.

403
00:32:17,500 --> 00:32:18,530
Ji will send someone

404
00:32:18,530 --> 00:32:20,340
to investigate from some different angles.

405
00:32:22,260 --> 00:32:22,930
Lu,

406
00:32:24,180 --> 00:32:25,580
I think the more cautious he gets,

407
00:32:26,220 --> 00:32:29,060
the more complicated this case is.

408
00:32:32,180 --> 00:32:33,540
Unfortunately, Da Hui is dead.

409
00:32:34,340 --> 00:32:37,180
We can't get more clues from this.

410
00:32:41,060 --> 00:32:42,260
What's Tai's situation?

411
00:32:43,940 --> 00:32:45,500
I checked his gun and the bullets.

412
00:32:45,900 --> 00:32:48,100
His alibi is solid.

413
00:32:48,860 --> 00:32:50,860
He's not the killer of Da Hui, most likely.

414
00:32:51,580 --> 00:32:53,410
Hua City Police Department also agrees.

415
00:32:57,940 --> 00:32:59,290
We can't find any clue

416
00:33:00,180 --> 00:33:01,700
from such a big case.

417
00:33:06,980 --> 00:33:07,900
It seems from now on,

418
00:33:09,220 --> 00:33:11,460
we need to start with Song Cai.

419
00:33:12,780 --> 00:33:13,540
Song Cai?

420
00:33:16,540 --> 00:33:18,020
What Da Hui said on the boat

421
00:33:18,020 --> 00:33:19,020
made me realized Song Cai

422
00:33:19,020 --> 00:33:20,500
is involved in this.

423
00:33:21,540 --> 00:33:23,020
I heard about his guy before,

424
00:33:23,020 --> 00:33:24,340
from Pala.

425
00:33:24,860 --> 00:33:26,060
I think after Da Hui died,

426
00:33:26,300 --> 00:33:28,490
he will slowly come in sight.

427
00:33:30,300 --> 00:33:32,100
Tell me. What's your plan?

428
00:33:35,180 --> 00:33:36,100
Time is up!

429
00:33:38,540 --> 00:33:40,260
I will stay here for a while,

430
00:33:40,260 --> 00:33:41,620
to convince them that I'm a drug dealer.

431
00:33:42,620 --> 00:33:44,890
Song Cai is also one of Liao Yongjia's targets.

432
00:33:45,460 --> 00:33:46,540
Start with him first.

433
00:33:47,860 --> 00:33:49,020
I got it.

434
00:33:50,620 --> 00:33:51,780
You. Seriously?

435
00:34:02,620 --> 00:34:05,810
[Liao Yongjia Inspector Office]

436
00:34:07,300 --> 00:34:07,900
Come in.

437
00:34:10,139 --> 00:34:10,730
Captain Liao,

438
00:34:11,060 --> 00:34:12,380
this is the reporter from Hua City Daily,

439
00:34:12,380 --> 00:34:13,420
Who has made the appointment with Deputy Director Sha.

440
00:34:13,420 --> 00:34:14,090
He came here to interview you.

441
00:34:14,090 --> 00:34:14,659
Come in.

442
00:34:17,780 --> 00:34:18,290
Sit down, please.

443
00:34:24,020 --> 00:34:24,860
Sorry,

444
00:34:25,460 --> 00:34:26,460
I don't accept banners.

445
00:34:27,500 --> 00:34:29,500
I have a few questions for you.

446
00:34:30,489 --> 00:34:31,500
What questions?

447
00:34:33,699 --> 00:34:35,530
About the murder at the abandoned shipyard.

448
00:34:35,980 --> 00:34:36,940
Why the police announced

449
00:34:36,940 --> 00:34:38,420
that the case is closed

450
00:34:38,420 --> 00:34:39,780
when the killer hasn't been found?

451
00:34:41,020 --> 00:34:43,090
These are all related to the conflicts among the groups of the drug dealers.

452
00:34:43,980 --> 00:34:45,060
We Drug Enforcement Investigators

453
00:34:45,380 --> 00:34:47,380
will get prepared to close the case first.

454
00:34:47,900 --> 00:34:50,780
About the murder of Da Hui,

455
00:34:50,780 --> 00:34:52,900
we've already got several suspects,

456
00:34:53,580 --> 00:34:55,300
who have been sent to other departments.

457
00:34:55,820 --> 00:34:56,820
Who do you want to be the killer?

458
00:35:02,900 --> 00:35:04,660
According to the information I received,

459
00:35:05,100 --> 00:35:07,140
it seems that besides Dai Hui,

460
00:35:07,340 --> 00:35:08,980
there were only Liang Long and his gang at the scene.

461
00:35:09,540 --> 00:35:10,380
Therefore,

462
00:35:10,660 --> 00:35:12,980
do you think Liang Long killed Da Hui?

463
00:35:13,380 --> 00:35:14,300
There's no evidence of that.

464
00:35:14,860 --> 00:35:16,940
But we won't rule out the possibility.

465
00:35:20,950 --> 00:35:24,640
[Zhang Xian The second in command of South Asian Gang]

466
00:35:21,660 --> 00:35:22,580
Officer Liao,

467
00:35:31,060 --> 00:35:33,140
Mr. Cai has seen your hard work.

468
00:35:35,660 --> 00:35:37,780
And he won't blame you for Da Hui's death.

469
00:35:38,300 --> 00:35:39,610
But he is very curious to know

470
00:35:40,100 --> 00:35:41,580
who will be your next target?

471
00:35:45,860 --> 00:35:47,170
I heard that big batch of drugs

472
00:35:47,170 --> 00:35:49,020
were handed out by you.

473
00:35:49,690 --> 00:35:50,940
Are you trying to find out

474
00:35:50,940 --> 00:35:52,460
every one

475
00:35:52,900 --> 00:35:54,300
who was involved?

476
00:35:58,540 --> 00:35:59,660
This is the police station.

477
00:36:01,460 --> 00:36:03,570
These questions are not from me.

478
00:36:04,180 --> 00:36:05,940
I have to report to Mr. Cai.

479
00:36:06,700 --> 00:36:08,780
So please, give me an accurate answer.

480
00:36:10,100 --> 00:36:10,780
No, I'm not.

481
00:36:14,060 --> 00:36:14,860
That's good.

482
00:36:42,420 --> 00:36:44,980
Mr. Cai has sent you to save me.

483
00:37:50,980 --> 00:37:52,300
You really won't go with me?

484
00:37:56,140 --> 00:37:57,450
I've decided to stay.

485
00:37:58,380 --> 00:37:59,380
You can't stay here.

486
00:37:59,660 --> 00:38:00,780
It's too dangerous here.

487
00:38:01,460 --> 00:38:02,260
Tai,

488
00:38:02,490 --> 00:38:04,100
it is over now.

489
00:38:04,380 --> 00:38:05,700
And you know

490
00:38:05,900 --> 00:38:08,220
staying here is the best choice for me.

491
00:38:18,900 --> 00:38:19,540
Okay.

492
00:38:20,260 --> 00:38:21,300
But you have to promise me

493
00:38:21,900 --> 00:38:23,180
you won't make contact with Chen Mo.

494
00:38:26,220 --> 00:38:27,100
Why?

495
00:38:29,810 --> 00:38:31,660
Because now it's not just the drug dealers who want him dead.

496
00:38:32,380 --> 00:38:33,980
The police want to kill him too.

497
00:38:35,620 --> 00:38:36,460
The police?

498
00:38:36,940 --> 00:38:38,100
Why do you think that?

499
00:38:39,420 --> 00:38:40,730
Because I found this.


